HEADWORD: Optician
<hw>Op*ti"cian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>opticien</ets>. See <er>Optic</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>One skilled in optics.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
